Steps to initialize DMA :
There are 2 DMA modules in STM32f4/f7 DMA1 and DMA2. 
       STEPS:
       1. Enable clock access to DMA [RCC->AHB1ENR |= DMA1EN]
       2. Disable all DMA1 streams. [DMA1_Stream6->CR &= ~DMA_S_EN]
       3. Clear all interrupt flags of Streamx.[DMA1->HICR |= ]
       4. Set the destination buffer.[DMA1_Stream6->PAR = dst]
       5. Set the source buffer. [DMA1_Stream->M0AR = src]
       6. Set length.[DMA_Stream->NDTR = len]
       7. Select Streamx channel.[DMA_Stream6->CR = CHSEL4]
       8. Enable memory increment. [CR->]
       9. Configure transfer direction.[CR->]
       10. Enable direct mode and disable FIFO.[DMA_Stream6->FCR = 0]
       11. DMA Transfer complete register [CR->TCIE]
       12. Enable DMAx Streamx.[CR->EN]
       13. Enable UART transmitter for DMA.[UART->CR3->DMAT/DMAR]
       14. DMA interrupt enable in NVIC.[NVIC_EnableIRQ(DMA1_Stream6_IRQn)]
